theorem Topology.frontier_eq_closure_inter_closureCompl
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    frontier (A : Set X) = closure A ∩ closure (Aᶜ) := by
  classical
  simpa [frontier] using
    (Topology.closure_inter_closureCompl_eq_closure_diff_interior (A := A)).symm

theorem Topology.frontier_eq_closure_diff_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    frontier (A : Set X) = closure A \ interior A := by
  rfl
